The abbess of the monastery gathered the nuns:
"I have terrible news to tell you, sisters. A male spirit visited our monastery.
All the nuns:
- Ah!
One vote:
- Hee-hee-hee!
The Abbess continues:
"A condom was found in our garden.
Nuns:
- Ah!
One vote:
- Hee-hee-hee!
The Abbess:
- There is a hole in the condom!
Nuns:
- Hee-hee-hee!
One voice:
- Ah!
